            <p>Join us for a casual cult party / housewarming / post-wedding / summer solstice celebration on our front lawn (<a href="/dresscode">dresscode</a>).</p> 
            <ul>
                <li class="pl-0">Rain or shine, Saturday, June 21st at our house a.k.a. "The Pizza Hut":</li>
                <li><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/ZW1zYkR4GJhDqrW26" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">19 Arnold Drive</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/ZW1zYkR4GJhDqrW26" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Woodstock, New York, 12498</a></li>
                <li class="pl-0">Pizza, frivolity, and bacchanalia.</li>
                <li class="pl-0">Festivities begin at 3:30 and end at 8:00.</li>
                <li class="pl-0">
                    Friday margaritas: If you're in town on Friday, join us for dinner at 
                    <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/YtMiLEV8aQWhtYpQ8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Santa Fe</a> at 7pm. 
                    It’s $40/per person for food and there will be a cash bar. To RSVP, please Venmo @carolineonmulberry $40 for each person you're paying for and write their names in the “What's This For?” line.  Don't have Venmo?  Text Caroline at 609-577-0117 to let her know you're coming and pay her in a different manner.
