            <h2 class="title is-2">Getting here</h2>
            <p><span style={{fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Parking will be limited,</span> so please carpool and use a designated driver!</p>
            <p>You'll need to coordinate your own transportation. Uber/Lyft can be pricy and are not as widely available up here. If you are looking for a taxi, try calling/texting Marlene at 845.443.1723 or Kent at 941.586.4792.</p>
            <p>
